{"tid":1053934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話說今日去睇戲 比人check學生證","createTime":"2019-03-09T12:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T14:08:45.000Z","uid":197852,"like":49,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78aa6390d85902421280d82564d36d1ec75e35a9","tid":1053934,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:50:57.000Z","msg":"今日約咗班friend一齊睇死亡無限loop2<br />\n點之入場既時候條mk見我地買學生飛就好臭串話要check 我地學生證<br />\n我當時呆咗一呆<br />\n我地成班大學生已經著咗soc頹tee<br />\n大大隻字寫HKU,CU,UST 連shitty 仔都無<br />\n但個mk仔話個個都買得啦<br />\n咁我地唯有拎學生證比佢睇<br />\n仲問翻佢邊間U <br />\n點知個mk即刻頭耷耷眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地上電梯嗰時仲回頭恥笑佢<br />\n<br />\n原來媽咪真係無呃我 勤力讀書真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973804561084076c7f07cbbea0e75f648024b756","tid":1053934,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"你嗰件係禾含?"},{"pid":"ae777b8de26c218a6402139cda195c0bcf6eb6cf","tid":1053934,"uid":197852,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"973804561084076c7f07cbbea0e75f648024b756","tid":1053934,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"你嗰件係禾含?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"咁cheap我著U記唔好？"},{"pid":"41e4a70f075b5da6aa91ea70cd34a4ca140b086c","tid":1053934,"uid":63419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7debf41e393a7c3cbb1d8c1ddb05a533ec434dc0","tid":1053934,"uid":197852,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"各位DSE雞做人定做狗就睇DSE<br />\n就算大家都係掃街<br />\n揸住學位掃都威過無學位既人"},{"pid":"9cb931da315c2237bf249a044beafa99ff27c516","tid":1053934,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41e4a70f075b5da6aa91ea70cd34a4ca140b086c","tid":1053934,"uid":63419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"唔通禾含型？"},{"pid":"6283cb8becad0ed79fd257138d6cccc11598c5e6","tid":1053934,"uid":218626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"想通了, 即將和社會接軌 <br />\n<br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5ToPfi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5ToPfi.png&h=4edb89f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人)<br />\n<br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，?務局聯繫。 <br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。 <br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司權力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"ee74fab7c4fe84e796461bff83a6840ff69c3837","tid":1053934,"uid":218626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:58:04.000Z","msg":"大學是神聖，認真交流學會的地方。 <br />\n不是講政治，追女仔，講粗口&hellip;&hellip;的地方。 <br />\n能獲得大學學位，就應該好好珍惜，因為你代表著社會的未來，是少數知識分子之一，22%人左右。而不是成為偏激份子，不然將來的社會使GG 了。 <br />\n我的未來，大學之路~要理性繼續走。"},{"pid":"125c53020497bb264e7d9d120d630e2e0a57793a","tid":1053934,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:58:05.000Z","msg":"咪又係比人check"},{"pid":"62eca6b1117959e8974fd74eb913a14d04ee84ca","tid":1053934,"uid":197852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"125c53020497bb264e7d9d120d630e2e0a57793a","tid":1053934,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:58:05.000Z","msg":"咪又係比人check"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"比毅進警 check 我都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f752771be23b14dc69c84311672665e710d09e0","tid":1053934,"uid":156130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62eca6b